column17:
'desc': [u'

Himalaya Gentle Baby Wipes (24 Pieces) Price: Rs.70

Gentle and skin friendly baby wipes can come in handy for various reasons. While travelling changing your infant's nappy and making sure she is cleaned properly and her skin is sanitized will be a lot easier with the Himalaya Gentle Baby Wipes. These wet wipes are effective in cleansing the skin by killing all the germs.

These Himalaya Gentle Baby Wipes are hypoallergenic and hence delicate on a newborn's fragile skin. Enriched with a formula that contains natural extracts of Aloe vera and Indian Lotus these wet wipes clean the baby's skin effectively. The Himalaya Baby Wipes are clinically tested and hence safe to be used on a baby's skin. This wipe will leave your little one's skin moisturized and a pleasant fragrance will linger on the skin that will make the child feel clean and fresh.

']
